{"tid":2373374,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港A貨金正恩　被寄送BB彈槍　再廿警上門搜屋　以無牌藏彈拘捕","createTime":"2021-01-20T11:47:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T17:39:51.000Z","uid":261647,"like":266,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"6ade08f080bcd48f4721789811ba4afdf42b52b4","tid":2373374,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:47:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/studioincendo/posts/2812277142353690\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstudioincendo%2Fposts%2F2812277142353690&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1IaxR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=0417b017\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/studioincendo/posts/2812277142353690</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hPC3MbV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhPC3MbV.png&h=e2c08dc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：Studio Incendo<br />\n<br />\n經常出現於遊行現場的「A貨金正恩」Howard X 今日在FB發聲明，指2020年10月28日有10多名警察上門搜屋，並以涉嫌無牌管有彈藥拘捕他。他指警方稱去年4月有一把BB彈槍寄到他家中，但自己從未收過。他認為這是一次任意拘捕，針對他過去諷刺中共。<br />\n<br />\nHoward 被帶到警署後他質疑警方這次拘捕行動毫無根據，「他們卻強調這次命令是來自更高級的部門，他們只是打工」<br />\n<br />\nHoward 指自己至今仍未被起訴，保釋後每六星期到警署報到，今日則是12月後另一個報到日。<br />\n<br />\nCredit: 2nd photo Howard X FB"},{"pid":"29b138fa02cb25ade54846f790e3345d321d2824","tid":2373374,"uid":70964,"like":21,"dislike":7,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"6ade08f080bcd48f4721789811ba4afdf42b52b4","tid":2373374,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:47:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/studioincendo/posts/2812277142353690\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstudioincendo%2Fposts%2F2812277142353690&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1IaxR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=0417b017\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/studioincendo/posts/2812277142353690</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hPC3MbV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%